It's admired by
the people of the city,
despite its creepy appearance.</c>

00:11:14.050 --> 00:11:15.580
Give it a rest.

00:11:15.580 --> 00:11:18.190
If you're the newspaper guy,
I already told you we don't want it.

00:11:22.530 --> 00:11:23.950
Who is it?!

00:11:23.950 --> 00:11:26.850
My father just died of a stroke,

00:11:26.850 --> 00:11:30.190
and we're still busy with 
everything that follows.

00:11:30.190 --> 00:11:31.830
Could you come back another time?

00:11:32.650 --> 00:11:34.840
Y-You're...

00:11:37.550 --> 00:11:38.930
Jo...

00:11:39.590 --> 00:11:41.970
Joseph!

00:11:41.970 --> 00:11:45.200
You finally came back, Joseph!

00:11:45.200 --> 00:11:47.220
I was waiting for you this whole time!

00:11:47.220 --> 00:11:51.290
I've been so sad and lonely since my dad died.

00:11:51.290 --> 00:11:54.570
I can't believe you showed up 
at a time like this, Joseph!

00:11:55.310 --> 00:11:58.570
I love you, I love you, I love you, 
I love you, I love you, I love you,

00:11:58.570 --> 00:12:03.650
I love you, I love you, I love you, 
I love you, I love you, I love you!

00:11:58.780 --> 00:12:02.950
I hate to disappoint you, 
but I'm not Joseph Joestar.

00:12:03.650 --> 00:12:04.320
Huh?

00:12:04.320 --> 00:12:06.420
Take a good look. No wrinkles.

00:12:06.420 --> 00:12:09.430
Oh... Now that you mention it...

00:12:11.120 --> 00:12:12.830
You're pretty young!

00:12:12.830 --> 00:12:14.650
Good grief...

00:12:14.650 --> 00:12:18.360
I'm Joseph's grandson. My name's Jotaro Kujo.

00:12:18.680 --> 00:12:20.840
O-Oh, really?

00:12:20.840 --> 00:12:23.420
Ask Josuke for the rest of the details.

00:12:23.820 --> 00:12:26.720
I hate annoying conversations.

00:12:27.550 --> 00:12:30.400
I'm here to see Josuke. Is he here?

00:12:35.860 --> 00:12:38.510
I'm asking you where Josuke is.

00:12:38.510 --> 00:12:43.820
Huh? Oh! Josuke hasn't come 
home from school... yet.

00:12:44.120 --> 00:12:46.820
I see... Then I'll be back tonight.

00:12:46.820 --> 00:12:47.820
Huh?

00:12:47.820 --> 00:12:49.700
You're leaving already?

00:12:52.540 --> 00:12:53.580
Oh, yeah...

00:12:54.080 --> 00:12:55.460
About your father...

00:12:55.460 --> 00:12:56.260
Huh?

00:12:56.840 --> 00:12:58.340
It's a shame.

00:12:58.340 --> 00:13:01.790
If Joseph Joestar had come to this city,

00:13:01.790 --> 00:13:05.010
he would have protected you as best
he could from the dangers to come.

00:13:05.650 --> 00:13:07.660
But he's old now.

00:13:07.660 --> 00:13:10.010
I can't let him come here.

00:13:10.730 --> 00:13:12.680
I'm here in his place.

00:13:19.030 --> 00:13:21.260
I just can't feel at ease.

00:13:21.260 --> 00:13:23.650
The bow and arrow that 
Angelo was talking about...

00:13:24.580 --> 00:13:29.010
In documents the Speedwagon Foundation
obtained regarding the witch, Enyaba...

00:13:30.570 --> 00:13:34.160
She's holding the bow and arrow.

00:13:34.690 --> 00:13:38.140
They give ordinary people the power of a Stand.

00:13:38.710 --> 00:13:40.800
Damn, that's unbelievable...

00:13:44.110 --> 00:13:45.290
No Trespassing

00:13:44.370 --> 00:13:46.470
Are you insane?

00:13:46.470 --> 00:13:47.950
Let him go.

00:13:46.490 --> 00:13:55.380
No Trespassing

00:13:47.950 --> 00:13:51.200
My father bought this house.

00:13:51.200 --> 00:13:53.920
Don't go digging around here.

00:13:53.920 --> 00:13:55.390
Never do it again!

00:13:55.390 --> 00:13:57.700
I'm not talking about that.

00:13:57.700 --> 00:13:59.980
I'm telling you to let go of him, bastard.

00:14:00.470 --> 00:14:03.030
If you don't let him go now,
I'm gonna get pissed off.

00:14:03.030 --> 00:14:06.050
Come on, now. "Bastard" is a bit much, ain't it?

00:14:06.050 --> 00:14:11.260
Calling someone you just met a bastard 
right in front of their house...

00:14:11.260 --> 00:14:13.620
Do you even know how to talk to people?

00:14:14.180 --> 00:14:18.000
Well, I know how to shut that mouth of yours.

00:14:19.810 --> 00:14:20.410
Stab

00:14:21.380 --> 00:14:22.880
What?!

00:14:24.910 --> 00:14:25.920
Bro?!

00:14:27.390 --> 00:14:30.560
Do you wanna know why
I shot him with the arrow?

00:14:30.560 --> 00:14:33.780
Because that guy is Josuke Higashikata.

00:14:33.780 --> 00:14:36.390
Oh, really? He is?

00:14:37.580 --> 00:14:40.430
Since he defeated Angelo,

00:14:40.430 --> 00:14:43.650
that means he's a Stand user
who'll be trouble for us, too.

00:14:44.430 --> 00:14:47.860
A Stand user?! You two are Stand users?!

00:14:47.860 --> 00:14:51.870
Okuyasu! Make Josuke Higashikata disappear!

00:14:55.360 --> 00:14:56.520
Koichi...

00:14:57.500 --> 00:15:01.350
Hmph! I was hoping I could
make him into a Stand user

00:15:01.350 --> 00:15:03.430
that I could use like the others,

00:15:03.430 --> 00:15:04.750
but I guess that's not happening.

00:15:04.750 --> 00:15:06.510
He's gonna die.

00:15:10.510 --> 00:15:12.100
M-Move!

00:15:12.100 --> 00:15:15.510
I can still heal his wounds 
with my Shining Diamond!

00:15:16.450 --> 00:15:17.600
No!

00:15:23.940 --> 00:15:28.280
Josuke Higashikata! I, Okuyasu
Nijimura, will make you disappear

00:15:28.280 --> 00:15:30.530
with my The Hand!

00:15:36.430 --> 00:15:37.580
Here we go!

00:15:45.130 --> 00:15:48.630
If you don't move, I'm seriously 
going to mess up your face.

00:15:50.700 --> 00:15:53.070
You're pretty fast.

00:15:53.820 --> 00:15:55.640
Hey, Okuyasu.

00:15:55.970 --> 00:16:00.990
Using a Stand is the same as 
driving a car or riding a bike.

00:16:00.990 --> 00:16:03.860
Dipshits with no skill or guts

00:16:03.860 --> 00:16:06.220
will get scared and maneuver like crap,

00:16:06.220 --> 00:16:09.720
no matter what kind of 
monster machine they ride.

00:16:10.060 --> 00:16:11.320
Bro...

00:16:11.320 --> 00:16:14.470
Please don't say things 
that'll piss me off too much.

00:16:14.470 --> 00:16:17.660
This bastard's much faster than I thought.

00:16:17.660 --> 00:16:20.580
We're not messing around here, Okuyasu!

00:16:20.910 --> 00:16:26.980
The Stand that you acquired, The Hand, 
gives me chills just thinking about it.

00:16:26.980 --> 00:16:28.940
You'd better be serious when you use it.

00:16:29.470 --> 00:16:34.090
Make sure you kill Josuke Higashikata,
who defeated Angelo, no matter what!

00:16:34.090 --> 00:16:37.650
He's bound to get in our way.

00:16:38.130 --> 00:16:39.720
I know—

00:16:39.720 --> 00:16:42.760
Ah! I was talking!

00:16:42.760 --> 00:16:44.480
Th-That's not fair!

00:16:44.730 --> 00:16:47.160
You're pretty stupid, aren't you?

00:16:47.160 --> 00:16:48.880
What? Why?!

00:16:48.880 --> 00:16:49.990
Why do you think tha—

00:16:51.330 --> 00:16:52.900
I told you to move.

00:16:54.500 --> 00:16:55.590
Koichi!

00:16:57.140 --> 00:16:59.490
Thank goodness. You're still alive.

00:16:59.490 --> 00:17:01.160
Then I can still save...

00:17:01.160 --> 00:17:04.670
That's it! You're gonna pay for that!

00:17:04.670 --> 00:17:06.630
I told you to move!

00:17:06.630 --> 00:17:08.460
Get any closer and you'll really piss me off!

00:17:08.460 --> 00:17:12.570
Take your best shot, if you can!

00:17:18.530 --> 00:17:22.020
He's got way too much
confidence in his right hand.

00:17:23.770 --> 00:17:24.740
This isn't good.

00:17:24.740 --> 00:17:27.960
I've got a really bad feeling 
about that right hand of his...

00:17:29.360 --> 00:17:32.470
Let go of my right hand, you little shit!

00:17:32.470 --> 00:17:33.860
Yeah, it's his right hand!

00:17:39.850 --> 00:17:40.400
Swoop

00:17:44.180 --> 00:17:45.870
Why, you...

00:17:45.870 --> 00:17:48.570
Don't you dare run away, Josuke!

00:17:48.570 --> 00:17:51.090
Don't abandon your friend like that!

00:17:51.090 --> 00:17:54.070
There's something up with 
that right hand of yours.

00:17:54.070 --> 00:17:57.130
Something's telling me it's not safe.

00:17:57.830 --> 00:18:00.680
Think about that after you're dead!

00:18:00.680 --> 00:18:02.600
Here I go!

00:18:02.600 --> 00:18:05.600
Koichi... Just hang on a little longer...

00:18:05.930 --> 00:18:08.940
No  passing

00:18:08.940 --> 00:18:11.940
What's with that gate? 
Something's wrong with it...

00:18:12.390 --> 00:18:14.690
No... passing?

00:18:22.700 --> 00:18:26.370
Stop walking backwards, you dumbass.

00:18:26.370 --> 00:18:29.650
You're getting farther away from your buddy.

00:18:30.150 --> 00:18:32.210
Come a bit closer!

00:18:33.860 --> 00:18:36.260
That's it... The "tres" is missing.

00:18:36.260 --> 00:18:40.430
I bet your Stand's right hand

00:18:40.430 --> 00:18:42.130
scraped it off, right?

00:18:42.130 --> 00:18:44.640
It has the power to scrape 
away its surroundings.

00:18:44.370 --> 00:18:45.500
No  passing

00:18:47.020 --> 00:18:49.970
That's right, Josuke Higashikata!

00:18:49.970 --> 00:18:53.750
Whatever this right hand 
grabs gets scraped away.

00:18:53.750 --> 00:18:55.940
And the parts that don't get scraped away...

00:18:56.560 --> 00:18:59.660
close together, so it looks like nothing changed.

00:18:59.660 --> 00:19:02.880
As for the part that gets scraped away...

00:19:02.880 --> 00:19:07.410
Even I don't know where it ends up!

00:19:10.590 --> 00:19:14.380
I can do this to guys who try to run away, too.

00:19:20.040 --> 00:19:23.390
I scrape away the space between us! And then...

00:19:26.770 --> 00:19:28.480
See? You came right to me.

00:19:28.480 --> 00:19:30.730
You could call it teleporting!

00:19:35.880 --> 00:19:40.440
This is the power of the Stand 
even my bro fears, The Hand!

00:19:40.440 --> 00:19:42.950
You can't run away anymore,

00:19:42.950 --> 00:19:44.870
Josuke!

00:19:45.620 --> 00:19:48.290
No matter where you go, you're...

00:19:48.290 --> 00:19:49.790
always...

00:19:50.560 --> 00:19:52.790
within my reach!

00:19:57.830 --> 00:19:59.010
So weak!

00:19:59.320 --> 00:20:03.260
You really beat Angelo like this?

00:20:11.690 --> 00:20:14.870
I guess you just don't get that it's no use.

00:20:14.870 --> 00:20:17.480
You're the one who's stupid!

00:20:19.110 --> 00:20:22.680
Now die, Josuke!

00:20:21.660 --> 00:20:24.450
You really are stupid, aren't you?

00:20:24.450 --> 00:20:25.120
Why?!

00:20:36.440 --> 00:20:36.740
Smack

00:20:36.860 --> 00:20:37.080
Crash

00:20:38.020 --> 00:20:38.330
Kaboom

00:20:42.720 --> 00:20:46.220
That was close. Okuyasu Nijimura, huh?

00:20:46.540 --> 00:20:49.930
That's a pretty great and terrifying Stand.

00:20:51.900 --> 00:20:54.360
I'll be in trouble if he wakes 
up and tries to attack.

00:20:54.760 --> 00:21:00.230
I guess I should strangle him a bit, 
just to make sure he stays knocked out.

00:21:00.230 --> 00:21:03.460
It'll put the feeling of defeat in his soul, too.

00:21:03.460 --> 00:21:04.850
One, and...

00:21:05.990 --> 00:21:07.450
K-Koichi's...

00:21:12.210 --> 00:21:15.790
That's enough, you bastard!

00:21:26.180 --> 00:21:30.480
This arrow is very precious. 
It's the only one there is.

00:21:31.000 --> 00:21:33.600
It's my precious objective.

00:21:35.410 --> 00:21:37.650
I just <i>have</i> to retrieve it.

00:21:41.720 --> 00:21:44.320
According to Angelo's story,

00:21:44.320 --> 00:21:48.470
it's this bow and arrow that 
unleashed DIO's Stand powers.

00:21:49.010 --> 00:21:51.450
There's no doubt about it.
That unleashed The World...

00:21:52.750 --> 00:21:57.300
And after Enyaba died,
someone obtained the bow and arrow,

00:21:57.300 --> 00:22:01.340
and is creating more Stand users in Morioh.

00:22:03.740 --> 00:22:07.470
I've got to hurry and destroy
that bow and arrow...

00:22:08.120 --> 00:22:10.180
To make sure a villain more evil than DIO

00:22:10.690 --> 00:22:16.690
doesn't appear with a Stand 
more powerful than The World.

